/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24893,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/29\/quds-salat-masjid-aqsa\/","url_meta":{"origin":26517,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jerusalem: Sins forgiven by praying at Masjid al-Aqsa","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen Solomon, son of David, peace and blessings be upon him, built the Sacred House, he asked Allah Almighty for the three things throughout. Solomon asked Allah Almighty for judgment coinciding with His judgment, and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32867,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/23\/what-is-tazkiyat-al-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":26517,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tazkiyah: What is purification of the soul?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mu\u2019awiyah reported: A man said, \u201cWhat is purification of the soul?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThat one knows Allah Almighty is with him wherever he is.\u201d Source: al-Mu'jam al-S\u0323aghi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 555 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":